```plantuml
@startuml hyeonsangjeon_AWS-LLM-SageMaker

actor User
participant "Streamlit UI" as UI
participant "Prompter" as Prompter
participant "KoLLMSageMakerEndpoint" as Endpoint
participant "Amazon Opensearch" as Opensearch
participant "FAISS" as FAISS

User -> UI: Interact with Chatbot
UI -> Prompter: Build Prompt
Prompter -> Endpoint: Send Prompt
Endpoint -> Opensearch: Retrieve Documents
Opensearch -> Endpoint: Return Documents
Endpoint -> FAISS: Perform Vector Search
FAISS -> Endpoint: Return Similarity Scores
Endpoint -> Endpoint: Generate Response
Endpoint -> UI: Return Response
UI -> User: Display Response

@enduml
```